    "longBusinessSummary": "Phuong Nam Cultural Joint Stock Corporation produces and trades in books, magazines, cultural products, and stationery. It offers national literature and foreign language books; tapes and discs under the Phuong Nam Phim brand; and school supplies, educational toys, and souvenirs under the Phuong Nam Bookstore and its e-commerce site comprising Nhasachphuongnam.com. The company also provides Bookish.vn, an online literary platform that publishes content on news in the publishing world, events, or seasonal promotions offered by Phuong Nam Bookstore; literary discussions, including weekly recommendations, in-depth reviews, and interviews with authors; cultural phenomena and social issues; short stories, serial works, and book excerpts; and publishes latest books in Vietnam and internationally. In addition, it operates bookstores; acts as an agent for publishing books and newspapers; engages in the wholesale and retail of books, newspapers, magazines, video tapes, toys, etc.; manufactures and trades in tapes, paper and paper products, and school equipment and supplies; offers services for commercial advertising and cinemas; prints on packages, binding, gilding, and coloring covers; produces films; post-production services; and organizes performances, as well as leases premises. The company was formerly known as Phuong Nam Cultural Product Manufacturing and Trading Joint Stock Company and changed its name to Phuong Nam Cultural Joint Stock Corporation in May 2004. Phuong Nam Cultural Joint Stock Corporation was founded in 1982 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
